description:
Choose the wrong private email provider and you could lose years of data or compromise your privacy, here's how Proton Mail, Tuta, and Fastmail actually compare. From zero-knowledge encryption, speed differences, pricing, to discovering which provider fits your specific needs. Whether you want maximum privacy, a complete ecosystem, or premium performance, this comparison covers the real-world trade-offs.
